{"tid":2339726,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"富士山12月仍無積雪情況不尋常！網民擔心或為火山爆發先兆","createTime":"2020-12-25T01:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T01:58:41.000Z","uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f52653f470de1e5b954d51df3065fd73cec1b51d","tid":2339726,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T01:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/holiday.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/60469582.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fholiday.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F60469582.jpg&h=074175d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本富士山喺12月冬季時節仍無積雪，情況罕見極不尋常，日本本州北部地區早前降雪量破紀錄，但富士山山頂仲未冠雪，有日本網民擔心係山體升溫嘅原因，令富士山有可能火山爆發。<br />\n<br />\n日本北邊早前受暴雪影響，降雪量更破紀錄，而位於靜岡縣、山梨縣嘅富士山，今年12月仍無積雪。<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">12月21日(月)朝の富士山全景です。\n山頂付近はマイナス20度。\n麓でも風が強いので、頂上では更に凄そうですね。\n雲ひとつなく、いいお天気です。\n富士市では0度でした。\nほんと、雪が無いですね&hellip;。 pic.twitter.com/D52vJ6TM2Z\n\n&mdash; た　く　み (@ihakita) December 20, 2020</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n富士山2020年於9月28日冠上初雪，比舊年提早24日，不過後來氣溫上升令積雪融化。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/holiday.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/481be332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fholiday.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F481be332.jpg&h=4323a96c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到冬季12月，富士山仲未積雪冠上雪冠，令唔少日本網民感到憂慮。有網友擔心係因為山體升溫，令積雪馬上融化，代表富士山或會有火山爆發危機。<br />\n<br />\n實際上富士山最後一次爆發係300年前嘅1707年，雖然富士山仍係一座活火山，自2011年日本大地震以嚟，火山活動亦有加劇，但暫時仲係安全水平。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/holiday.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/139f61c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fholiday.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F139f61c2.jpg&h=f162ee76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本氣象新聞Weathernews指，12月27~28日將有氣壓喺山谷中穿過，如果有足夠水氣，應該可以再次出現冠雪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://holiday.presslogic.com/article/216961/富士山-12月-無積雪-火山爆發-日本-冠雪\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.presslogic.com%2Farticle%2F216961%2F%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%B1%B1-12%E6%9C%88-%E7%84%A1%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%AA-%E7%81%AB%E5%B1%B1%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-%E5%86%A0%E9%9B%AA&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt6WONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=c3cdd324\" target=\"_blank\">https://holiday.presslogic.com/article/216961/富士山-12月-無積雪-火山爆發-日本-冠雪</a>"},{"pid":"e43e54fe06fbaeda9bcc5a2efe1cf496084a1a5b","tid":2339726,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T01:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPjt778.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPjt778.jpg&h=9fcbf750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果tatsuki嘅預言夢真係咁準，根據佢嘅規則81年發夢打後加上15年，冇嘅再加15年，咁富士山真係有機會下年2021爆發。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QUKpikQgAOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQUKpikQgAOk&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt6WONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=a1a754da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QUKpikQgAOk</a>"},{"pid":"65a1514bd8530ef21d4cb03b743a6b43c1c52155","tid":2339726,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e43e54fe06fbaeda9bcc5a2efe1cf496084a1a5b","tid":2339726,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T01:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPjt778.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPjt778.jpg&h=9fcbf750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果tatsuki嘅預言夢真係咁準，根據佢嘅規則81年發夢打後加上15年，冇嘅再加15年，咁富士山真係有機會下年2021爆發。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QUKpikQgAOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQUKpikQgAOk&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt6WONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=a1a754da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h